  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK644">
<l>tiṟaṉaṟintu colluka collai yaṟaṉum </l>
<l>poruḷu mataṉiṉūuṅ kil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Understand the qualities (of your hearers) and (then) make your speech; for superior to it, there is neither virtue nor wealth.</l>
            </lg>
